name: THE PLACE WHERE I FOUND (my) LIGHT
description:
I GOT ILLUMINATED BY MACHU PICCHU

I DID LONG TRAVELS BELIEVING THAT I WAS GOING RIGHT: 
MY PICTURES WOULD GIVE ME A LONG ROAD TO WALK.
I REALIZED THERE, I NEED NO OCCIDENTAL SECURITY TO BELIEVE IN.

YOU KNOW?
IS SOMETHING LIKE LOVE
LIKE LOVE SOMEBODY THAT LOVES YOU TOO,
OR LIKE ART,
OR FATE,
OR YOUR OWN HUNCH OF BEING IN THE PLACE THAT YOU WANT TO BE.

BY THE WAY, I STILL TRUST MYSELF 
I´M STILL WANTING TO GROW UP IN THE TRUTH.
THAT ONE THAT I FOUND TRAVELING.
